      "translations": {
        "en.hubeali": [
          "Sahl Bin Ziyad, from Ali Bin Asbaat, raising it, ",
          "‘He<sup>asws</sup> said: ‘Oiling the two eyebrows removes the headache’."
        ],
        "en.sarwar": [
          "9. Sahl ibn Ziyad has narrated from Ali ibn Asbat in a marfu‘ manner has said the following: “He (the Imam), ‘Alayhi al-Salam, has said, ‘Applying viola oil to one’s eyebrows dispels headaches.’” "
        ]
